sentences.english: Now we have a vending machine that we can turn on and off.
sentences.chinese: 現在我們有了一臺可以開啓和關閉的自動售貨機。

sentences.english: This is where a vending machine distributor can really help you.
sentences.chinese: 這是一個自動售貨機經銷商真能幫助你。

sentences.english: It's not till late afternoon that the electrician began to repair the winch.
sentences.chinese: 直到下午很晚電工纔開始修起貨機。

sentences.english: I need the change for the automat.
sentences.chinese: 我想從自動售貨機上買東西。
即使是40噸重的安通娜12型貨機也一樣。

sentences.english: This vending machine is provided by a food company from the UnitedKingdom.
sentences.chinese: 人工售貨機是由英國的一家食品公司安置在這裏的。

sentences.english: When will you begin to install the cargo winches?
sentences.chinese: 你們何時開始安裝起貨機？

sentences.english: The vending machine is out of order again.
sentences.chinese: 這臺自動售貨機又壞了。

sentences.english: And the guy that made this, he made a slot machine out of Lego.
sentences.chinese: 做這個的人，他拿樂高做了個投幣自動售貨機。

sentences.english: Candy-filled vending machines and soda coolers are mostly gone.
sentences.chinese: 糖果和蘇打水滿自動售貨機冷卻器大多不見了。

sentences.english: I just lost another 50 cents in this stupid vending machine.
sentences.chinese: 這個破自動售貨機又吞了我50美分。

sentences.english: my team is working on a spice vending machine for spices.
sentences.chinese: 我們的團隊正在設計一個調味料的自動售貨機。

sentences.english: The schools typically receive a percentage of the sales from these machines.
sentences.chinese: 學校一般都會從這些售貨機收出的食物中提成。

sentences.english: The accident is the second fatal crash of a cargo plane on takeoff within six weeks.
sentences.chinese: 這是六個星期以來第二起貨機起飛時發生墜毀事故。

sentences.english: The capstan power is inter locked with the power of the No. 4 hold cargo winch.
sentences.chinese: 絞纜機電源與四倉起貨機電源是連鎖的。

sentences.english: Japan has more than 5.5 million vending machines, note validators and game-playing machines.
sentences.chinese: 日本有550萬臺自動售貨機，驗鈔機和遊戲機。

definition: Hong Kong Dragon Airlines (operating as Dragonair), Hong Kong-based international airline

the rear (tail) of a plane etc
